      "content": "idk im just really uncomfortable lol. i dont really want to go to the doctor or the er if it's just indigestion, it's a huge hassle and expensive. do u think the arm pain is definitely just from the reflux? it's kinda weird but i feel like if it was serious i'd know. i'll probably just take a couple of tums and try to sleep it off. that's fine right?",
