      "content": "a pulmonary embolism sounds scary but u said it's unlikely right? i really think this is just the pizza. if i take like 4 tums at once instead of just 1 or 2, do u think that would help clear it up faster so i can just sleep? i'd rather just deal with it at home tonight.",
